msgstr "再次强调，若核心或任何核心模块有做过修改应重新启动系统，以及任何受影响的Binary应重新执行。"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/cutting-edge/_index.adoc:217
msgid ""
"Only the [.filename]#GENERIC# kernel can be automatically updated by "
